title: Sloan - Smeared & One Chord To Another

I wish I had their 2nd album, Twice Removed (awarded the Indie Album of the Century award or something like that, lol).  I gave up on them after they moved from Halifax to Toronto, since they moved their Murderecords label with them, leaving a lot of local sh!t out of luck...

If anyone has Plumtree, I'd be so grateful if you shared it with me...
